text: Acleris proximana is a species of moth of the family Tortricidae. It is found in South Korea and China. The wingspan is about 15 mm.Check List of the Tribe Tortricini (Lepidoptera: Tortricidae) in Northeast china, with Two Newly Recorded Species from China ==References== Category:Moths described in 1927 proximana Category:Moths of Asia
